children.name: Rules
children.text:
This paddle used in making alchemy is treated as a +1 quarterstaff.
The wielder of this staff increases the spell DC of all necromancy spells by +1. The staff has 3 charges and can cast the following spells. It regains a charge when a creature of CR 2 or higher is brought to zero hit points within 30 feet of Moon Mash.
1 charge: Wither and Bloom
1 charge: Inflict Wounds (level 2)
2 charges: Animate Dead
